By Andile Mngxitama When comrades allowed Ramaphosa to stand as President of ANC they didn’t know: 1. He is an alleged spy?
2. Was funded and groomed by the Oppenheimers since the 1970s?
3. He removed President Zuma and Thabo Mbeki from critical positions during negotiations without a mandate.
4. His New Dawn campaign was funded and openly directed by white monopoly capital?
5. He called the police to murder workers in Marikana?
6. A book by Gayton Mckenzie detailed some of the above allegations? How can you allow such a man to be your President? Emang Pele asomblief… Andile Mngxitama is the President of Black First Land First (BLF), a radical black consciousness organization. 